    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "A fantastic opportunity to own a dependable, well-cared-for vehicle that's ready to serve you for many miles to come! This car presents really well \u2014 the exterior shows only minor wear consistent with normal everyday use, and the paint retains a nice shine overall. The interior is clean and comfortable, and mechanically the car has been properly maintained and drives with confidence. If you're looking for a reliable daily driver with plenty of life left in it, this one is well worth your attention!",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
