      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in truly mint condition \u2014 a rare find that genuinely lives up to the designation. The exterior is flawless, with paint that retains its original luster, no scratches, dents, or blemishes of any kind, and chrome and trim pieces that shine as if the car just rolled off the showroom floor. The interior is equally immaculate \u2014 seats, carpeting, headliner, and all surfaces show zero meaningful wear, with every control, gauge, and feature functioning exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean and well-maintained, the mechanicals are in excellent working order, and there are no warning lights, unusual noises, or deferred maintenance items to speak of. This is the kind of car that turns heads and inspires confidence \u2014 a true collector-quality example that has been exceptionally well cared for throughout its life.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 one of the finest examples you'll find on the used market. The exterior is virtually flawless: the paint retains a deep, rich luster with no visible scratches, chips, or swirl marks, and all body panels are perfectly aligned. The interior is equally impressive, showing no meaningful wear on the seats, carpets, dashboard, or headliner \u2014 everything looks and feels fresh. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean and well-maintained, with all mechanical systems functioning exactly as they should. The tires have substantial tread remaining, the brakes are in excellent shape, and all electronics, lights, and accessories work perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to own a used vehicle that genuinely looks and drives like new.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is offered as a reliable, drivable used car with honest acknowledgment of its wear and imperfections. The exterior shows multiple scratches, a few small dents, and paint fading consistent with its age and use \u2014 nothing that affects drivability, but visible cosmetic wear that a buyer should expect. The interior is functional with normal signs of use, including some worn upholstery and minor scuffs on the trim. Mechanically, the car runs and drives as expected for its age, though it may benefit from routine maintenance in the near term. There are no major mechanical failures to report, but buyers should factor in the cosmetic condition and potential upcoming maintenance needs when considering this purchase. This is a solid everyday driver for a buyer who values function over appearance and wants an honest, fairly priced vehicle.",
      "price": 15000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Affordable & Honest \u2013 A Practical Pick for the Budget-Conscious Buyer! \ud83d\ude97\n\nLooking for a car that gets the job done without the premium price tag? This one might be just right! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives, but does show its age with some wear and minor imperfections you'd expect at this price point. It's not a showroom beauty, but it's a real, usable car that can serve as a reliable daily driver with the right expectations. Priced honestly to reflect its condition \u2014 what you see is what you get, and we're not hiding anything. A solid opportunity for a budget-savvy buyer! \ud83d\udd11",
      "price": 21000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    }
